{"tid":1162564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙嘴街頭舉機影人打架 男子遭打傷搶手機","createTime":"2019-05-20T02:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T03:05:07.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"486e44b791dae66ae98d2c54e06b8a4e854d8ecc","tid":1162564,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YR3B38G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYR3B38G.png&h=104edefe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmAQo8H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmAQo8H.png&h=b3d50277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員封鎖現場調。翁鈺輝攝<br />\n<br />\n早上8時半許，一名男子報稱在尖沙嘴加拿分道與金馬倫道交界，遭人襲擊搶劫，警員接報到場封鎖調查，將受傷男事主送院治理，暫時無人被捕。現場消息指，事發前有兩人在現場位置打架爭執，男事主見狀上前舉機拍攝，惹來兩人不滿，結果男事主被人打傷，兇徒再搶去其手機後逃之夭夭。"},{"pid":"dc425eda2070bd3018a82aa91bb676dcadc097fc","tid":1162564,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:58:33.000Z","msg":"花生友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91917d0694417b7bc9ecc4117d5426483e0fbf7f","tid":1162564,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc425eda2070bd3018a82aa91bb676dcadc097fc","tid":1162564,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:58:33.000Z","msg":"花生友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"佢做花生友唔夠專業, 呢D 情況真係唔好光明正大咁拍人打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849d66cdb71f119daf7e6ce83a55bf39fa95e2f6","tid":1162564,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:05:07.000Z","msg":"買部30pro遠距離影呀麻67<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /